message.body: When do you get here baby?
Just landed!! Should be there in the afternoon cuz baby has an eye doctor apt at 4
Oh my!!!!!!! Who's picking you up?
Jen!
Nice! Let me know when you're in town
This babt went all through the night, headache. But I met a really cute guy on the bus, exhanged numbers
Roughhhhhhh. We'll have to take it easy tonight - just one bottle of vino at lola's.
Ha!! U know it
At the appt then to gma. I'm thinking lola's around 630 - can I text u? Can tim join us?
Yayyyy! Welcome home! Yea that works for me. Not sure about Tim, Colin gets home today. I'll see what's up with him. :)
Oh that bitch colin who I love but flutters in and out of my life like a buTterfliiiii. He was SUPPOSED to hang out with me and kath...
Waiting for happy hoes at gmas. We can do the hot tub tonightttttt
Yea yea yea yea!
You know that youre in rural Minnesota when you go to taco johns to eat inside with the whole family... It's too early for cynicism I know. May be a little after 630.
Leaving my house in like 5 :)
Wait, for Lola's. You should meet us at taco john's then!
Kk - so after 630?
Ok!
I ended up spending the day with fam in Mankato. What are you doing?
I'm just about to run some errands in town, wrap, etc. Just sat around :):)
Everything ok chicken??
Yea, I'm fine. It's funny that you'd ask right then bc I was just thinking, "why do I feel unsettled?" and tried to calm myself.
It's a lot so I'm sure it's going to be more discomfort than not. But it's only going to get better. It's like that feeling when we think about fast fowarding
And looking back and saying "geez, I can't believe it was like that, makes me kinda gringe"...
Totally. You mean with friends and tim?
Just in general, more like being in nu and making it make sense
Yea, it's a transition. I was just hoping for a break.
Every time I come home I realize it's a transition. Just wait until you're in your bed in philly, you're gonna realize how that's home :)
Right, and find a way to be content in the interim
Do you want us to pick up any books? Tipping point?
Yes!!! Exactly what I need
Anything else?
I think that's it. U saved me xoxo
Omg. The whole galvin fam just did ALL of your partner moves
Yessssssssssssss everyone?
Jen isn't here but everyone did. Ryan and I held the square for 15. I'm a pro on top
15 minutes?? Whoaaaa. Even Kathy?
15 seconds. Cathy was a HOOT
Schells deer brand? Yeah or nay?
I think that's good... I got day drunk and ruined so I won't be drinking any. :/
Merry christmas eve martha - love you lots and lots
Much love and Christmas wishes! I hope I wasn't too much of a wet blanket last night. I didn't know how I was supposed to be and was also more interested in acting the opposite...
Don't worry about it! I was tired as well and I just wanted to curl up and watch movies. Also felt weird about amber being there and would have rather caught up
With al and everyone else
